{"tid":105114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（真人真事，唔係故仔）後樓梯結界","createTime":"2017-02-02T15:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T16:54:22.000Z","uid":75636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d816dcd9202ac7c92fc4465264968fb3709b835c","tid":105114,"uid":75636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"話說今日放完狗，諗住同隻狗跑下樓梯，幫隻狗減肥。<br />\n咁就跑到7樓，見隻狗無乜氣就諗住搭lift番屋企。<br />\n因為住棟大廈就分左單，雙數層既，咁我住12樓，就要行多上一層先有lift 搭。<br />\n正常7樓上一層就應該係8樓，咁就無望塊牌就推防煙門就出左去搵lift , 點知發現得一部lift(正常每層係有兩部）而且部lift係無上下制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上成層都無單位，無門口（除防煙門同lift）。<br />\n咁我就開始覺得唔對落，拿拿聲叫番隻狗行番去後樓梯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由走廊通去後樓梯係要經兩對防煙門先到，姐係防煙門之間係會有一個小空間。<br />\n咁我就企左係兩對門之間，並開左兩對門等隻狗可以拿拿聲走過黎去後樓梯。<br />\n咁奇妙既野就發生啦<br />\n我好肯定隻狗係走廊度，咁我就向走廊方向叫佢，但係佢竟然係後樓梯個邊走過黎我度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時無諗咁多 唔理三七廿一就同埋隻狗衝左上多一層。而當我上多一層先係8樓。姐係話我去左個層係7同8之間。個feel好似入左結界咁，定係話本身棟樓既設計係咁呢？<br />\n個種感覺好似再留多陣會出唔番黎咁。<br />\n想同下有冇巴打試過又係行後樓梯去左唔知邊到既地方？<br />\n利申：sor for 1999，住左廿年都唔知有空層"},{"pid":"1ae7c61d262bb1bcaab6bdabc475c9fb9a84b016","tid":105114,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:46:40.000Z","msg":"留名睇故"},{"pid":"aa08849fda2c29ea81c49824a212e8e37e359a0c","tid":105114,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"隻狗救咗你"},{"pid":"14bc59ec1622003dbbca7a3dcd9333d01b2f97fa","tid":105114,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:48:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d68f5db5ea783e6d21f9958060797df176474be","tid":105114,"uid":75636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻狗救咗你</blockquote><br />\n隻狗有時會望住一個位停左係到，唔知佢做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc33343a25fa0f60bdf76a2f07c3d5285bb248ee","tid":105114,"uid":75636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連防火層都唔知，樓主幼稚園畢業未？</blockquote><br />\n棟棟都有既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594a5de3941c2cdb27e410f9673540d513fc11d8","tid":105114,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"邊度先 我要探險 順便探埋樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bcc89f6ab481fb8da475078caff9830e949564","tid":105114,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:52:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c017e198be963d97e9cb2039e51050780a04a744","tid":105114,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"好刺激咁<br />\n組團探險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5803472284a3c7ef60dc8ea4e8f13aafbf773ce","tid":105114,"uid":59654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"隻狗仲係咪原本嗰隻???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38ceede2a22e065144a94619312db68df1d20e6","tid":105114,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"邊樹呀"},{"pid":"89e057ad096caeffa1d7f98128e96037a09686be","tid":105114,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻狗仲係咪原本嗰隻???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0b1ecf0818c7cf4638cfd158207dfdb193e6a9","tid":105114,"uid":58687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"